# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:13
translate french jez5_450455fc:

    # "It's Detective Rodriguez. I wonder if she's found something out about my dad."
    "C'est l'inspectrice Rodriguez. Je me demande si elle a découvert quelque chose sur mon père."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:16
translate french jez5_bea5e8cb:

    # pc "Hello?"
    pc "Allô ?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:18
translate french jez5_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/jez_hey.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_hey.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:19
translate french jez5_31f304d3:

    # det "Hey, [pcname]."
    det "Salut, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:20
translate french jez5_704218da:

    # pc "Did you find anything?"
    pc "Tu as trouvé quelque chose ?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:22
translate french jez5_dd220c64:

    # det "What? Oh! About your dad?"
    det "Quoi ? Oh ! À propos de ton père ?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:24
translate french jez5_e8fe8a8c:

    # det "Oh God, no I'm sorry. I wasn't calling about your dad, but I can understand why you'd think that."
    det "Oh mon Dieu, non, je suis désolée. Je n'appelais pas à propos de ton père, mais je comprends pourquoi tu as pensé ça."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:25
translate french jez5_1559f8f9:

    # det "With me being a detective and on your dad's case and all."
    det "Vu que je suis inspectrice et que je m'occupe de l'affaire de ton père, tout ça."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:26
translate french jez5_8c3ac124:

    # det "God, I'm a horrible detective aren't I?"
    det "Mon Dieu, je suis une inspectrice épouvantable, n'est-ce pas ?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:27
translate french jez5_a807c23e:

    # pc "No, I don't think so. What did you call for then?"
    pc "Non, je ne crois pas. Pourquoi m'as-tu appelée alors ?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:30
translate french jez5_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/jez_5_1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_5_1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:31
translate french jez5_0a63889f:

    # det "Well, I had kind of a rough day and I wanted to talk to somebody."
    det "Eh bien, j'ai eu une journée un peu difficile et j'avais envie de parler à quelqu'un."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:33
translate french jez5_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/jez_5_2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_5_2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:34
translate french jez5_ea09e714:

    # det "And you were nice to me in the past, when we went out for drinks."
    det "Et tu as été gentille avec moi par le passé, quand on est allées boire un verre."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:36
translate french jez5_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice 'voices/jez_5_3.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_5_3.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:37
translate french jez5_307d2b53:

    # det "And I don't really have anybody else to talk to."
    det "Et je n'ai vraiment personne d'autre à qui parler."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:39
translate french jez5_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice 'voices/jez_5_4.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_5_4.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:40
translate french jez5_0f2cd5d3:

    # det "So I was wondering if you would want to just talk some?"
    det "Alors je me demandais si tu voudrais bien discuter un peu ?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:46
translate french jez5_47059538:

    # det "You're right. This was a mistake, I'm sorry."
    det "Tu as raison. C'était une erreur, je suis désolée."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:47
translate french jez5_ec16f7c0:

    # det "I won't bother you any more until I have information on your dad."
    det "Je ne te dérangerai plus tant que je n'aurai pas d'informations sur ton père."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:48
translate french jez5_07fc1b9f:

    # det "Bye, [pcname]."
    det "Au revoir, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:52
translate french jez5_5429a27f:

    # "She hangs up and I lie down to go to sleep."
    "Elle raccroche et je m'allonge pour dormir."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:53
translate french jez5_ceaf3431:

    # "I can hardly believe that she wants to call me and dump her problems on me. Don't I have enough of my own to deal with?"
    "J'ai du mal à croire qu'elle veuille m'appeler pour me déverser ses problèmes. N'ai-je pas assez de miens à gérer ?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:54
translate french jez5_0a396100:

    # "I mean, my dad is missing and it doesn't seem like she's doing much of anything to find him."
    "Je veux dire, mon père a disparu et on dirait qu’elle ne fait pas grand-chose pour le retrouver."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:55
translate french jez5_a9441b54:

    # "Maybe I was a little harsh with her, but she needs to do her damn job."
    "J’ai peut-être été un peu dure avec elle, mais elle doit faire son fichu boulot."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:56
translate french jez5_437235da:

    # "I fall asleep, still upset about the whole thing."
    "Je m’endors, toujours contrariée par toute cette histoire."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:62
translate french jez5_9f04dd80:

    # det "My Chief is yelling at me all the time because I haven't been able to track down this meth manufacturer."
    det "Mon chef me crie dessus tout le temps parce que je n’ai pas réussi à retrouver ce fabricant de méthamphétamine."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:63
translate french jez5_2edb985d:

    # det "It's like, I'm trying. There's only so much I can do."
    det "C'est pas comme si j'essayais pas. Je fais tout ce que je peux."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:64
translate french jez5_d637e4b1:

    # det "I spend most of my day on stakeouts watching drug handoffs."
    det "Je passe la majeure partie de mes journées en planque à surveiller des transactions de drogue."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:65
translate french jez5_b65d63fc:

    # det "Or interrogating people, trying to push them into telling me something."
    det "Ou à interroger des gens, à essayer de les pousser à me dire quelque chose."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:66
translate french jez5_e4fde77f:

    # det "But nobody's giving anything up and I'm running out of leads."
    det "Mais personne ne lâche rien et je suis à court de pistes."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:67
translate french jez5_45b6d6aa:

    # det "There's only two detectives on this case. A big meth ring and just two of us."
    det "On n'est que deux inspecteurs sur cette affaire. Un gros réseau de méthamphétamine et juste nous deux."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:68
translate french jez5_77a9cef6:

    # det "I mean Skyhill is a small town, so I get it, but I need more help here."
    det "Je veux dire, Skyhill est une petite ville, donc je comprends, mais j’ai besoin de plus d’aide ici."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:69
translate french jez5_72d52a4d:

    # det "I wish we could call in the state police, or the FBI or something, but the Chief won't have it. Says we have to handle this ourselves."
    det "J’aimerais qu’on puisse faire appel à la police d’État, ou au FBI, ou quelque chose comme ça, mais le chef ne veut pas en entendre parler. Il dit qu’on doit s’en occuper nous-mêmes."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:70
translate french jez5_d8b3de1e:

    # det "But there's only so much I can do. I have other cases too - like your dad's - that I'm having to neglect because of this meth thing."
    det "Mais je ne peux pas tout faire. J’ai d’autres affaires aussi – comme celle de ton père – que je dois négliger à cause de cette histoire de méthamphétamine."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:72
translate french jez5_88d7e875:

    # det "And today I had to raid the house of this methhead."
    det "Et aujourd’hui, j’ai dû faire une descente chez cette toxicomane."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:73
translate french jez5_d5874b9e:

    # det "It was horrible. This woman, her house was disgusting. Her baby, a three-year-old girl, was sitting in the middle of a bunch of filth naked."
    det "C’était horrible. Cette femme, sa maison était répugnante. Son bébé, une petite fille de trois ans, était assise nue au milieu d’un tas d’ordures."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:74
translate french jez5_2823a872:

    # det "And I had to take this child, who was screaming and crying that she didn't want to leave her mom, and give the child to protective services."
    det "Et j’ai dû prendre cette enfant, qui hurlait et pleurait parce qu’elle ne voulait pas quitter sa maman, et la confier aux services de protection de l’enfance."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:75
translate french jez5_e5dd6ea8:

    # det "The girl will probably have a better life in foster care than she would have with her mother, but who knows. She could end up with some abusive assholes or something."
    det "Cette fillette aura sans doute une vie meilleure en famille d'accueil qu'elle n'en aurait eue avec sa mère, mais qui sait ? Elle pourrait bien se retrouver chez des salauds violents ou quelque chose du genre."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:76
translate french jez5_5e97fe72:

    # det "That little girl's life is messed up no matter what happens now."
    det "La vie de cette petite fille est gâchée, quoi qu'il arrive maintenant."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:77
translate french jez5_a1286de7:

    # det "And it just makes me so sad."
    det "Et ça me rend tellement triste."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:78
translate french jez5_89052a8b:

    # pc "I'm sorry. That's awful."
    pc "Je suis désolé. C'est horrible."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:80
translate french jez5_97380cd0:

    # det "So I get the woman back to the station and start interrogating her."
    det "Je ramène donc la femme au poste et je commence à l'interroger."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:81
translate french jez5_3e4784a1:

    # det "She's going to jail for at least five years for possession, probably will get a child endangerment charge as well, but she won't give up her dealer."
    det "Elle va prendre au moins cinq ans de prison pour possession, elle sera probablement aussi accusée de mise en danger d'enfant, mais elle refuse de dénoncer son dealer."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:82
translate french jez5_19e09092:

    # det "I don't fucking get it."
    det "Je n'y comprends rien, putain."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:83
translate french jez5_59760784:

    # det "She's scared that something will happen to her family if she snitches."
    det "Elle a peur qu'il arrive quelque chose à sa famille si elle balance."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:84
translate french jez5_c0f63ffe:

    # det "Spits in my face, calls me a pig. I wanted to beat her fucking head in."
    det "Elle me crache au visage, me traite de porc. J’avais envie de lui fracasser la tête."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:85
translate french jez5_c36e96d1:

    # det "Then I get chewed out by the Chief because I didn't get anything out of her."
    det "Et puis je me fais engueuler par le chef parce que je n’ai rien obtenu d’elle."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:87
translate french jez5_2288ac26:

    # det "And that was my day."
    det "Et voilà, c’était ma journée."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:88
translate french jez5_2074c381:

    # det "I'm just so tired of all of it. I want to find this meth manufacturer and shut that shit down."
    det "J’en ai tellement marre de tout ça. Je veux trouver ce fabricant de méthamphétamine et mettre fin à cette merde."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:90
translate french jez5_3a7bef84:

    # "I think about telling her about the bunker that Izzy had sent me to."
    "Je pense à lui parler du bunker où Izzy m’avait envoyée."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:91
translate french jez5_35c47a4d:

    # "But I'm not sure that is really what she's looking for."
    "Mais je ne suis pas sûr que ce soit vraiment ce qu’elle cherche."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:92
translate french jez5_7dda6c8a:

    # "Plus, I'm not sure if me and Izzy might get in some serious trouble for our part in whatever they were doing."
    "En plus, je ne sais pas si Izzy et moi risquons d’avoir de sérieux ennuis pour notre implication dans ce qu’ils faisaient."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:93
translate french jez5_9fcbf4b8:

    # "I may tell Jez about it later, but for now I stay quiet."
    "J’en parlerai peut-être à Jez plus tard, mais pour l’instant, je me tais."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:95
translate french jez5_6387c117:

    # "I think about telling her about the bunker that Reba had taken me to."
    "Je pense à lui parler du bunker où Reba m’avait emmené."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:96
translate french jez5_35c47a4d_1:

    # "But I'm not sure that is really what she's looking for."
    "Mais je ne suis pas sûr que ce soit vraiment ce qu’elle cherche."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:97
translate french jez5_306cf091:

    # "Plus, I'm not sure if Reba might get in some serious trouble for our part in whatever they were doing."
    "En plus, je ne sais pas si Reba pourrait avoir de sérieux ennuis à cause de notre implication dans ce qu’ils faisaient."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:98
translate french jez5_9fcbf4b8_1:

    # "I may tell Jez about it later, but for now I stay quiet."
    "Je lui en parlerai peut-être plus tard, mais pour l’instant, je me tais."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:99
translate french jez5_a3049ca4:

    # det "Anyway, thanks for listening to me vent."
    det "Bref, merci de m’avoir écoutée me défouler."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:100
translate french jez5_732596c5:

    # det "I needed to get all that off my chest."
    det "J’avais besoin de vider mon sac."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:101
translate french jez5_d957ecb7:

    # pc "You feeling better now?"
    pc "Tu te sens mieux maintenant ?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:103
translate french jez5_880af095:

    # det "A little, yeah."
    det "Un peu, oui."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:104
translate french jez5_566089d7:

    # det "You're a pretty good listener, [pcname]. Thank you."
    det "Tu sais bien écouter, [pcname]. Merci."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:105
translate french jez5_c46a0b54:

    # pc "Any time."
    pc "Quand tu veux."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:107
translate french jez5_1d1792a8:

    # det "I can be a good listener too, if you ever want to chat."
    det "Je sais aussi être à l'écoute, si jamais tu as envie de discuter."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:108
translate french jez5_d87a672d:

    # det "You could call me at nights and we could just talk or something."
    det "Tu pourrais m'appeler le soir et on pourrait juste parler ou autre chose."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:110
translate french jez5_b7c62ab4:

    # pc "That sounds good. I'll do that."
    pc "Ça me dit bien. Je le ferai."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:112
translate french jez5_fc19b673:

    # det "Good."
    det "Bien."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:114
translate french jez5_d41d8cd9_5:

    # voice 'voices/jez_5_5.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_5_5.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:115
translate french jez5_22567fb7:

    # det "Okay, [pcname], I better get to bed. Thanks for listening to me."
    det "Bon, [pcname], je ferais mieux d'aller me coucher. Merci de m'avoir écoutée."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:117
translate french jez5_d41d8cd9_6:

    # voice 'voices/jez_5_6.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_5_6.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:118
translate french jez5_22b369a9:

    # det "I'll talk to you later."
    det "On se reparle plus tard."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:119
translate french jez5_31e08f47:

    # pc "Okay, good night, Jez."
    pc "D'accord, bonne nuit, Jez."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:121
translate french jez5_d41d8cd9_7:

    # voice 'voices/jez_night.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_night.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:122
translate french jez5_8669dcbe:

    # det "Night."
    det "Bonne nuit."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:125
translate french jez5_52d6e3cf:

    # "We hang up and I get ready for bed."
    "On raccroche et je me prépare à aller me coucher."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:126
translate french jez5_73bafe8e:

    # "It must be hard having to deal with the things that she deals with, see the things that she sees every day."
    "Ça doit être dur de devoir gérer tout ce qu’elle doit gérer, de voir tout ce qu’elle voit tous les jours."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:127
translate french jez5_63d39c7b:

    # "I like that she is opening up to me though, becoming more friendly."
    "J’aime bien qu’elle s’ouvre à moi, qu’elle devienne plus amicale."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:128
translate french jez5_00f887ed:

    # "I actually really like her."
    "En fait, je l’aime vraiment bien."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez5.rpy:129
translate french jez5_c6ddf2e1:

    # "I fall asleep thinking about how I'd like to spend more time with her. Hopefully we'll get a chance soon."
    "Je m’endors en pensant à quel point j’aimerais passer plus de temps avec elle. J’espère qu’on en aura l’occasion bientôt."

